e4c84c37788bdc0f98f2b6c45ca497a3f8eac5b948ddf034c40ee12af0d1ac88d3ebf64dd146936f4f0f1b295c7fa7f3cd2854f85e2ec3dd546a8ccc716f3bdd  revert-fix-jagginess-for-activities-list-icons.patch"
